Welcome to My Blog!

 Apr 22, 2020

Apr 22, 2020

As a real estate professional, I know what’s happening every day in the area, specifically concerning home values and how these trends and developments will directly affect you. Even as this ongoing pandemic is changing our market, I’m out on the front lines to make sure that those changes are communicated to you.

Therefore, I plan to post  two helpful messages each month on this blog to keep you updated and help you stay on top of what’s happening in the community.

Thank you for taking the time to read this.

Even though the way we buy and sell homes is changing, I’m going to be here to help you through it. Let us know if you have any questions. 

Check back because content will be coming soon!

I’m determined to keep you updated on what’s going on with the real estate market.

    REALTOR®


    For over two decades Sylvia Lunsford has passionately served her clients by establishing rapport, building trust, and creating lasting partnerships. Her extensive background in real estate, finance, and marketing enables her to draw from a deep well of knowledge and life experience to help her clients make informed and intelligent decisions.

    A dynamic Realtor® with in-depth knowledge and a broad range of strengths makes her a standout leader in the Central Coast real estate market. Described by her peers and clients as caring, insightful and determined, Sylvia goes beyond expectations to serve. She is inherently attentive to clients’ goals, needs and desires, tirelessly assisting them at every point of the selling and buying process.

    Sylvia gained certification in 2009 as a Distressed Property Expert (CDPE), and also became a Certified Luxury Home Marketing Specialist (CLHMS) in 2010, a designation requiring verified property sales in the top 10% of the market.
